Necessary technical and financial assistance for the implementation of a national vision and Action Plan for the prevention and control of non-communicable diseases for the period 2014-2020 period. In particular: 
1. In improving the legal framework for tobacco control 
2. Promoting issues in tax policy at the governmental level. 
3. In the development of requirements for drawings / icons placed on the packaging of tobacco products; 
4. The planning. implementation and evaluation of pilot projects that contribute to health. which includes measures for tobacco control at the level of communities. schools. health facilities; 
5. In improving the services provided staff of primary health care for smoking prevention. counseling for smoking cessation. tobacco dependence treatment
